cls (1.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added universal installer script (install.sh) supporting all Linux distributions
  * Added support for Termux (Android) installation
  * Implemented case-insensitive command-line options (-h, -H, --help, --HELP, etc.)
  * Added all 8 case combinations as symlinks (cls, Cls, CLS, CLs, ClS, cLS, cLs, clS)
  * Fixed package manager fallback logic in installer
  * Updated README with multi-platform installation instructions
  * Improved error handling and user feedback in installer

